                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 892.001/78.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">King of Siam</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-12-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 1, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I extend to Your Majesty cordial felicitations on this auspicious occasion and
                    assure you of the friendship of the Government and people of the United States
                    and of their best wishes for the welfare of Your Majesty and the happiness of
                    the people over whom you have been called to reign.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. H. Taft.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
